          <h6 class="border-bottom border-gray pb-2 mb-0">What's in the App?</h6>
          <div class="media text-muted pt-3">
            <p class="media-body pb-3 mb-0 small lh-125 border-bottom border-gray">
              This is a Rails 6 (PostgreSQL) example todo and blog application that utilizes React, Coffeescript, jQuery &amp; Bootstrap to shape the frontend.
            </p><!-- .media-body -->
          </div><!-- .media -->
          <div class="media text-muted pt-3">
            <%= image_tag 'tayberry.svg', alt: 'Media', class: 'mr-2 rounded' %>
            <p class="media-body pb-3 mb-0 small lh-125 border-bottom border-gray">
              <strong class="d-block text-gray-dark">Free</strong>
              Donec id elit non mi porta gravida amo vidicus metu. Quipio udon <%= link_to('rando', randoms_path) %>, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus. Pellentesque nulla nisi, dapibus ut purus aliquam. Proin vel purus ut nulla sodales faucibus id ut lacus.
            </p><!-- .media-body -->
          </div><!-- .media -->
          <div class="media text-muted pt-3">
            <%= image_tag 'schnozberry.svg', alt: 'Media', class: 'mr-2 rounded' %>
            <p class="media-body pb-3 mb-0 small lh-125 border-bottom border-gray">
              <strong class="d-block text-gray-dark">Premium</strong>
              Lorem Ipsum elit non mi porta gravida y at egorial. Pellentesque nulla nisi, dapibus ut purus aliquam, semper lacinia purus. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus pulio, e te brute y tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus. Proin vel purus ut nulla sodales faucibus id ut lacus.
            </p><!-- .media-body -->
          </div><!-- .media -->
          <small class="d-block text-right mt-3">
            <%= link_to('Sign in', new_user_session_path) %> or <%= link_to("Sign up", new_user_registration_path) %>
          </small>
        </div><!-- .my-3 p-3 bg-white rounded shadow-sm -->
      </div><!-- .modal-body -->
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div><!-- .modal-footer -->
    </div><!-- .modal-content -->
  </div><!-- .modal-dialog -->
</div><!-- .modal -->
